rdf:Description.lla:note: Note in Log Book describes how he became ill with Smallpox on 22 December 1871, was taken to Gibraltar and hospitalised until he recovered and returned to the ship on 10 January 1872.
Note in Log Book describes how he became ill with Smallpox on 29 November 1871, was treated on board until he recovered and returned to his work on 23 December 1871.
